WEBVTT

00:00.468 --> 00:02.735
<i> PREVIOUSLY</i>
<i> ON "SECRETS AND LIES"...</i>

00:02.736 --> 00:05.003
HOW DID
THE FLASHLIGHT DITCH GO?
